TestNG -- unit test framework
	   -- Test Driven Development (TDD) framework

purpose -- design test cases in a systematic way
		-- good html reports
		-- different annotations
		-- can be defined as priority or sequence of test cases
		-- dependency
		-- grouping
		-- data provider
		
testing -- open source
JAR files

Also known as Java unit testing framework


How to install TestNG in Eclipse
*******************************************

Go to Help -- Marketplace -- Search for TestNG
Or Go to Install new software -- enter URL -- Install
